<h1>Pathology Without Borders: An Open-Source Approach to pathology Training and Collaboration</h1>
<p>OpenFlexure microscope telepathology monthly case-based learning sessions featuring expert-guided digital pathology education through collaborative virtual conferences</p>
</div>
<div class="session-info">
<div class="info-card">
<span class="icon">⏰</span>
<h3>Session Format</h3>
<p>60 minutes total<br/>50 min cases + 10 min Q&amp;A</p>
</div>
<div class="info-card">
<span class="icon">📋</span>
<h3>Cases Per Session</h3>
<p>4-5 carefully selected cases<br/>Progressive complexity</p>
</div>
<div class="info-card">
<span class="icon">🔬</span>
<h3>Digital Slides</h3>
<p>Available 1 week before<br/>for participant preview</p>
</div>
<div class="info-card">
<span class="icon">📹</span>
<h3>Access</h3>
<p>Live streamed sessions<br/>Recorded for review</p>
